    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル、どうしてそんなに無茶をするの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel, why do you do such reckless things?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>私や他の人を守れれば
それでいいと本気で思っているの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you really think everything will just be okay
if you're able to protect me and everyone else?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>誰かを守る為に自分が死ぬ事が
正しいとでも思っているの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you think it's okay for you
to die protecting someone?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……止めなくちゃ。
こんなの絶対に間違ってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You've got to stop this.
That way of thinking is completely wrong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
